    Decision
    Decision interface is used to determine the decision of player or NPC.
    EnemyAI
    EnemyAI class represents non-person character, which is controlled by the computer.
    ManagerOfCharacters
    ManagerOfCharacters represents Model from MVC design pattern.
    ManagerOfNPC
    ManagerOfNPC handles the creation of the NPC on the separate thread, which improves performance and independence of the process.
    Participant
    Abstract class representing a participant in the game.
    User
    User is class which inherits from abstract class Participant, also implements Decision, Serializable interfaces Stores and manages user's data with methods like setPassword, giveVote, voteFor.
    UserRecognition
    UserRecognition represents tool for extracting only necessary data during voting process
    VotingControl
    VotingControl controls the whole voting process, handles logic and data related to voting.
